          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（一名：《葡萄会》）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "主要角色"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妹妹：花旦"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "公子：小生"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "院子：丑"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丑公子：丑"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "情节"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "考剧本，仅表明一男扮为女之文武小生，为一丑角之公子强行霸抢，居然亦以花轿抬入之，方欲拜堂成亲，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "忽奉母命，至东庄外家探病。因将此新人，寄入花旦妹子房中。新人故作娇痴，其妹遂效乱点鸳鸯故事，代"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兄与之拜天地，送入洞房，乔作夫妇成婚。迨至入帐，彼假新人始露真相，且身藏镔铁剑，系为报仇来者。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "其妹被胁，且亦心爱其人，遂与重拜天地，为真夫妻。天将明，其兄归，敲久，入，遂为文武生所杀。二人"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "乃作计遁去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "注释"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "秦腔多大同小异之戏，又多没头没脑，始终不报名之弊。演至终场，只知为一小生一旦角，及其他某角某角"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "而已，如此剧亦然。至其戏情，又似《王老虎抢亲》，又似《乱点鸳鸯》，惟结局不同，中间又有与《梵王"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宫》相似处，此余所以谓其多大同小异也。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "根据《戏考》第三十四册整理"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（丑公子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "丑公子",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "花轿亮堂堂，打扮作新郎。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（丫鬟上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "禀大爷：花轿到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丑公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好。花轿穿堂而过。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "轿子穿堂而过。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四青袍、轿夫同上，过场，同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "禀大爷：大事不好了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丑公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只因东庄娘舅，身得重病，老夫人命你前去探病。去得早了便罢，若是去得晚\n了，将你新人送回，轿子打坏，我看你是去也不去。话说完了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丑公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丫鬟回来，丫鬟回来，商议商议。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我不管。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（丑公子叹。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "丑公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这是哪里说起。是我正要拜堂成亲，丫鬟报到：东庄娘舅，身得重病，命我前\n去探病。去得早了便罢，若是去得晚了，将我新人送回，轿子打坏，这便如何\n是好？有了，我不免到妹妹房中，商议此事，将新人寄在妹妹房中，等我探病\n回来，再拜堂成亲。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "丑公子",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为了这件事，去求有情人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丑公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此已是妹妹房外。待我叫门。\n吓，妹妹开门来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（妹妹上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "上房绣鸳鸯，金钗别凤凰。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "外面何人叩门？"
        },
        {
          "character": "丑公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哥哥到了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待妹妹与你开门。\n哥哥到了，请进。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丑公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妹妹请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哥哥请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丑公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妹妹请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哥哥来到妹子房中，为了何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "丑公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妹妹有所不知，是我要拜堂成亲，丫鬟报到：言说东庄娘舅身得重病。命我前\n去探病，去得早便罢，若是去得晚了，将我新人送回，轿子打坏。你看哥哥如\n何是好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "依哥哥主见？"
        },
        {
          "character": "丑公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "依哥主见，欲将新人寄在妹妹房中，等探病回来再拜堂成亲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哥哥讲的哪里话来，想你每日在大街之上抢掳民女。你的事情妹妹一概不管。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丑公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我与你乃是同胞兄妹，你收下了罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妹妹不管。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丑公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我的好妹子呀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丑公子",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "与妹妹对坐在秀阁，\n听为兄把话对你说：\n我探病回来好快乐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "将新人暂寄你房内、妹妹",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "哥哥讲说理不通，\n听妹妹把话说心中：\n有妹妹不管闲事情。"
        },
        {
          "character": "每日抢掳民间女、丑公子",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一见妹妹她不从，\n倒叫我背过身好不伤情。\n叫妹妹从下这事情。"
        },
        {
          "character": "走上前来双膝跪、妹妹",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一见哥哥跪楼枰，\n背转身来思想情。\n妹妹从下这事情。"
        },
        {
          "character": "走上前来双膝跪、妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哥哥请起。"
        },
        {
          "character": "走上前来快搀起、丑公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妹妹从下了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妹妹从下就是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丑公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "从下便好。我要探病去了。\n家院带马。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（院子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "晓得。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丑公子",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫家院带过马能行，\n到东家探病走一程。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（丑公子、院子同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一见哥哥出门庭，\n等候新人入房中。\n又听丫鬟报一声。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（丫鬟上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "禀姑娘：花轿到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，搀了新人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "晓得。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（丫鬟搀公子同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "与姑娘叩天喜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "上房侍奉老夫人去吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丫鬟",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（丫鬟下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丫鬟去了，待我先将秀阁门上了，再与新嫂嫂叙谈叙谈。\n新嫂嫂，你好。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我好。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "新嫂嫂你好大的嗓音。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姑娘有所不知，只因我母下世去早，留奴年小，是我每日啼哭，因此上把嗓\n子啼哭坏了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "新嫂嫂我来问你，你好大的脚。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姑娘，方才言道，母亲去世，是我每日与小玩童一处游玩，因此上把脚跑大\n了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这就是了。观见嫂嫂头上，盖头去了，看看她容貌如何。新嫂嫂，我家哥哥，\n因为何事，将你抢进府来，对我言说，我好搭救与你。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姑娘要听，听我道来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "未开言不由人泪流满面，\n点点的珠泪洒落胸前。\n我母女一同到庙前。\n他一心霸占奴要结良缘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "五月节起了那葡萄大会、你哥哥他见我容貌好、妹妹",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "嫂嫂对我讲一遍，\n思想起来恼心间。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请问新嫂嫂，今春多大了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴家今年一十八岁了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听新嫂嫂之言，与我家哥哥同岁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，嫂嫂看什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为何不见你家哥哥，哪里去了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我家哥哥，去到东庄娘舅那里探病去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今晚回来不回来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今晚打量不回来的多。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今晚不回来，岂不耽误奴家洞房花烛这事了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "新嫂嫂，不必如此，家中现存我哥哥衣帽巾，待我穿戴起来，替我哥哥一拜花\n堂。你看如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我想你也是个女子，我也是个女子，那如何使得？"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说使得就使得。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "从不得。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "从得。你坐了罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（妹妹入帐子换装，出。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妙吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "在洞房穿红衫头有顶戴，\n把一个女孩儿扮做秀才。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，新嫂嫂，请过来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姑娘讲说什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓嫂嫂，你看我扮得可像男子？"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我看小姑娘，扮的倒像个男子。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "像个男，好好好，你我二人拜天地。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我不拜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你过来罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今夜晚替哥哥来把堂拜，"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嫂嫂你拜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我不会拜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不会拜？我教导于你。要整整头，抖抖衣，这样就是拜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我会了，先要整整头，抖抖衣，就是这样拜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "太高了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这样？"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "太低。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，高了又高了，低了又低了。我我不会了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你不会，待我手搭手教导于你，就是这样拜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，就是这样拜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "对了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "咱二人手搀手同上金阶，\n我这里替哥哥来把堂拜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嫂嫂，拜天地呀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我不拜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你跪下罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "作一对好夫妻永不分开。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "今夜晚我与你来把堂拜，"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "咱二人全都是女中裙钗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你哥哥去探病今晚不在，"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "女孩家无本不难做买卖。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓嫂嫂，你看天不早，上床来罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姑娘前行，我随后就到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嫂嫂来呀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我不去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你还叫妹妹，拉拉扯扯的么。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，不要拉拉扯扯的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你等我来了。嫂嫂，你搀我起来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我才不搀你起。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你不搀我起来，我自己起来。吓嫂嫂，你看天已晚，你我上床来罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姑娘请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嫂嫂请呀。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（妹妹入帐内。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嫂嫂来呀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嫂嫂来呀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "今夜晚我与她上床安眠，\n怕只怕上床去洩了机关。\n管叫她一家命归黄泉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "我这里藏过了镔铁宝剑、妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嫂嫂快来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来了来了来了，呔！"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不、不、不、不、不、不好了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一见将军变了脸，\n他是男子变作女。\n我情愿与将军配成婚。"
        },
        {
          "character": "将军留下奴不死、公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "将军留下奴不死、公子",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姐苦苦对我讲，\n倒叫小子生了难。\n再拜天地入洞房。"
        },
        {
          "character": "将军留下奴不死、公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，入洞房。"
        },
        {
          "character": "走上前来忙搀定、妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，将军，适才不是入过洞房了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "方才入过不算，还要另入。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你看那时才入过洞房，他还不算。他、他、他、他、他、他、他、他还要另入。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不入。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我入是入你是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且慢，还要另拜天地。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军，方才拜过天地了，不必拜了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "方才拜过不算，还要另拜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你看方才拜过天地了，他、他、他、他、他、他还要另拜。\n呀哥哥，快快回来罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你拜是不拜？"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴拜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一拜泰山为媒证，"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "二祗黄河就澄清。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "泰山已倒人还在。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "黄河一去影无信。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（公子、妹妹同入帐内。丑公子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "丑公子",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "探病一心早回转，\n急急速速成姻缘。\n再叫妹妹听兄言。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丑公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此妹妹房外，待我来叫门。\n妹妹开门来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（公子、妹妹同出帐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "门外何人叫门？"
        },
        {
          "character": "丑公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "连兄的声音，也听不出来了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来是哥哥回来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丑公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哥哥少等，妹妹与你开门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丑公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是什么人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我是五殿阎君要儿的狗命。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（公子开门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（公子杀死丑公子。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不、不、不、不、不、不、不、不好了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一见哥哥丧了命……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（院子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "院子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不好，杀人了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（公子杀院子。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好不叫人痛伤情。\n再叫军家听分明。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀将军，那你将我哥哥杀死，你我二人哪里逃走？"
        },
        {
          "character": "回头便把将军唤、公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可说是，这、这、这、这、这、这有了，马老爷现在柴桑口赴宴，你我二人，\n逃往那里去住倒也好，你看如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军说好便好，将军请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小姐请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了，哥哥呀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，你与我走。"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我走。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（公子搀妹妹。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "妹妹",
          "line_type": "哭",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哥哥呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（公子、妹妹同下。）"
        }
